snippet.title: Music of 40K
snippet.description:
Curated grimdark music for your gaming pleasure.

You can use my soundscapes for non-profit projects (such as YouTube videos), just be sure to credit Music of 40K and include a link to the soundscape you used.

Song titles, albums, composers/performers, and image sources are credited in the description of every video. If you'd like more information about a specific track, you can contact me using the e-mail below.

If any composer, artist, or developer has an issue with an upload, use the email below to contact me and I'll happily take it down.
